Creates embedded videos from youtube and vimeo links

To install clone the following git url:
git://github.com/ednapiranha/Linkify.git

change to the directory linkify and type in the following on the command line:
easy_install linkify

To use:
from linkify import linkify

vimeo_link = linkify('http://vimeo.com/12345')
youtube_link = linkify('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbCd123')